snippet.title: Baby Bulldog [2020] Full Movie | Tara Reid | Dean Cain | Calhoun Koenig
snippet.description:
Animal-lover Amber desperately wants a dog to love. When she falls for Shadow, she takes on her family and city hall to fight for her new best friend in a race against the clock.

Directed by Angela McCulley, Joel Paul Reisig
Starring Tara Reid, Dean Cain, Calhoun Koenig
